data.description: * New asking price * Aerial Video. Vacant! Awesome Farm House Style Four Bedroom Three Bath Home with a Wood Burning Fireplace and Wrap Around Screened Porch! This homesite site is well off the road so it's perfect for nice and quiet living. Large kitchen! Plenty of Solid wood cabinets! Large family room. Large sunlit insulated windows! Metal roof and vinyl siding! Hardwood floor, some vinyl flooring. Separate Living room, kitchen, dining room and a family room. One full bath down stairs. 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths upstairs. Features several pocket doors for added convenience. An in-line gas water heater that delivers instant hot water and saves you money. Wired for security. 2 year old AC. Irrigated. You'll enjoy your wrap around porch with porch swing. Half of the wrap around porch is fully screened on the kitchen side. Out back is an air conditioned 2019, 620 sq ft metal shop with concrete floor, wired with 100 amp service. Historic City of Sopchoppy has a City Park on the Sopchoppy River where you can swim, launch a boat and go fishing! Sopchoppy has a new pavilion park across from the Historic RR Depot. Sopchoppy has an annual Worm Grunting Festival with Live music, Food trucks and arts and craft vendors. Also a monthly Community Market, and annual Fireworks show. The Railroad Depot is the center of attention during the several Festivals. Schools, the Bay and Beaches are within minutes. Ochlockonee State Park RV Camping Right Down the Road! Lock box at side door. Must make an appointment to show.
